name: Maree  (human)
content: Maree was a human female and the daughter of Imperial General Skarhorn. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, she accompanied her mother and father to an Imperial Complex on the planet Garel where the general made a speech to mark the opening of a munitions factory. During the speech, Maree's mother praised Skarhorn's speech and stated to Maree that she must be proud of him.
